<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata xmlns=""><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="22785270"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="死奏憐音、玲瓏ノ終"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="nayuta"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Scattered Destiny"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="130727530"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="Azusa-mikan"/></metadata></head><body dur="00:00.000"><div xmlns="" begin="00:16.698" end="00:00.000"><p begin="00:16.698" end="00:20.288" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:16.698" end="00:17.761">それでも人は</span><span begin="00:18.590" end="00:20.288">醜くも生きようとする</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就算如此 人们也想丑陋地生存着</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so re de mo hi to wa、mi ni ku mo i ki yo u to su ru</span></p><p begin="00:22.959" end="00:27.518" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:22.959" end="00:23.888">それを私は</span><span begin="00:25.876" end="00:27.518">とても美しいと思う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对此 我却觉得那是如此的美丽</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so re wo wa ta shi wa、to te mo u tsu ku shi i to o mo u</span></p><p begin="00:37.731" end="00:41.886" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:37.731" end="00:39.501">記憶の音色は風に運ばれ、</span><span begin="00:40.424" end="00:41.886">空へと舞い上がり</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">记忆的音色随风而动 飞舞于空</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ki o ku no ne i ro wa ka ze ni ha ko ba re、so ra e to ma i a ga ri</span></p><p begin="00:43.994" end="00:46.226" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:43.994" end="00:44.949">雨に打たれる事も</span><span begin="00:44.943" end="00:46.226">なく自由に舞い踊り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">未经暴雨摧残 自由地舞蹈着</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a me ni u ta re ru ko to mo na ku ji yu u ni ma i o do ri</span></p><p begin="00:48.687" end="00:50.076" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L5">短い生を謳歌する<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">歌颂着短暂的人生</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mi ji ka i na ma wo o u ka su ru</span></p><p begin="01:06.317" end="01:11.750" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="01:06.317" end="01:07.586">廻れ</span><span begin="01:08.043" end="01:09.194">廻れ</span><span begin="01:09.634" end="01:11.750">報われぬ</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:06.393" end="01:11.866"><span begin="01:06.393" end="01:07.904">(願えども</span><span begin="01:07.904" end="01:09.539">願えども</span><span begin="01:09.539" end="01:11.866">願い叶わず)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">祈祷、祈祷、愿不得实现</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">nega e domo nega e domo nega i kana wa zu</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">轮回、轮回、不得报应</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ma wa re ma wa re mu ku wa re nu</span></p><p begin="01:12.870" end="01:18.511" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="01:12.870" end="01:14.269">道を</span><span begin="01:14.597" end="01:15.799">紡ぐ</span><span begin="01:16.062" end="01:16.586">我が</span><span begin="01:17.018" end="01:18.511">子等</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:12.923" end="01:18.309"><span begin="01:12.923" end="01:14.630">(走れどただ</span><span begin="01:14.630" end="01:16.021">走れども</span><span begin="01:16.021" end="01:18.309">辿り着けずに)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">奔跑、奔跑、却从未到达</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hasi re do tada hasi re domo tado ri tu ke zu ni</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN"> 开辟这条道路的芸芸众生啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hasi re do tada hasi re domo tado ri tu ke zu ni yo</span></p><p begin="01:18.917" end="01:24.777" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="01:18.917" end="01:20.870">其の物</span><span begin="01:20.870" end="01:22.532">語を</span><span begin="01:22.532" end="01:24.777">風に乗せ</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:19.326" end="01:24.954"><span begin="01:19.326" end="01:20.855">(贖えど</span><span begin="01:20.855" end="01:22.542">贖えど</span><span begin="01:22.542" end="01:24.954">罪は消えずに)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">救赎、救赎、罪没有消除</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">agana e do agana e do tumi ha ki e zu ni</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">请将那故事乘着风</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so no monogatari wo kaze ni no se</span></p><p begin="01:25.754" end="01:31.203" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:25.754" end="01:27.333">いつか</span><span begin="01:27.333" end="01:28.989">空</span><span begin="01:28.989" end="01:31.203">へ葬ろう</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:25.825" end="01:31.201"><span begin="01:25.825" end="01:27.525">(廻れどただ</span><span begin="01:27.525" end="01:29.048">廻れども</span><span begin="01:29.048" end="01:31.201">終は視得亡い)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">徘徊、徘徊、看不到终点</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mawa re do tada mawa re domo tui ha si doku na i</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在未来的某一天把它埋葬到天空吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">i tsu ka so ra e ho u mu ro u</span></p><p begin="01:46.445" end="01:52.113" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:46.445" end="01:49.021">足跡鼓動は</span><span begin="01:49.482" end="01:52.113">終わりに向かい始まる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">脚步声都向着结束而开始</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a shi a to ko do u wa o wa ri ni mu ka i ha ji ma ru</span></p><p begin="01:52.716" end="01:58.701" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:52.716" end="01:53.700">其れでも</span><span begin="01:54.448" end="01:55.321">人は</span><span begin="01:56.107" end="01:58.701">此方へと歩いて来る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使如此 人们没有停下走向这里的步伐</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so no re de mo hi to wa ko no ka ta e to a ru i te ku ru</span></p><p begin="01:59.337" end="02:05.157" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="01:59.337" end="02:00.334">歪な</span><span begin="02:01.015" end="02:02.133">憂世を</span><span begin="02:02.631" end="02:05.157">呪い悔やめど求めて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">诅咒着千变万化的扭曲世间 虽然后悔也不停追求着</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hi zu na yu u yo wo no ro i ku ya me do mo to me te</span></p><p begin="02:05.795" end="02:11.490" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="02:05.795" end="02:06.903">其れでも</span><span begin="02:07.486" end="02:08.443">何も</span><span begin="02:09.080" end="02:11.490">手にする事は出来亡い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">最终却仍然一无所得</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so no re de mo na ni mo te ni su ru ko to wa de ki na i</span></p><p begin="02:12.924" end="02:15.671" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="02:12.924" end="02:14.214">蹴落とされ</span><span begin="02:14.214" end="02:15.671">殴られて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">被排挤 被殴打</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">shu u o to sa re na gu ra re te</span></p><p begin="02:16.390" end="02:19.450" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15">雨に打たれ泣いて崩れ落ちて<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">被雨淋 流下了崩溃的泪水</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a me ni u ta re na i te ku zu re o chi te</span></p><p begin="02:19.450" end="02:25.000" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="02:19.450" end="02:22.082">渇く喉で叫んでも</span><span begin="02:22.804" end="02:25.000">戦えなくて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使嘶哑地喊叫 也无法战斗</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ka wa ku no do de sa ke n de mo ta ta ka e na ku te</span></p><p begin="02:26.085" end="02:28.427" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="02:26.085" end="02:27.451">奪い取られ</span><span begin="02:27.451" end="02:28.427">支配され</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">被掠夺 被支配</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">u ba i to ra re shi ha i sa re</span></p><p begin="02:29.341" end="02:32.373" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18">転がり落ち血を流していても<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">甚至跌倒得血流不止</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ko ro ga ri o chi chi wo na ga shi te i te mo</span></p><p begin="02:32.485" end="02:37.639" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="02:32.485" end="02:35.097">立ち上がり繰り返し</span><span begin="02:35.599" end="02:37.639">求め叫ぶ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">也会一次次站起来 追求着 呐喊着</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ta chi a ga ri ku ri ka e shi mo to me sa ke bu</span></p><p begin="02:40.392" end="02:46.012" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="02:40.392" end="02:41.959">詠え</span><span begin="02:41.959" end="02:43.595">詠え</span><span begin="02:43.595" end="02:46.012">報われぬ</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:40.461" end="02:45.999"><span begin="02:40.461" end="02:42.014">(願えども</span><span begin="02:42.014" end="02:43.543">願えども</span><span begin="02:43.543" end="02:45.999">願い叶わず)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">祈祷、祈祷、愿不能实现</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">nega e domo nega e domo nega i kana wa zu</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">咏唱、咏唱、不得报应</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">e i e e i e mu ku wa re nu</span></p><p begin="02:46.895" end="02:52.457" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="02:46.895" end="02:48.500">道を</span><span begin="02:48.500" end="02:50.126">歩む</span><span begin="02:50.126" end="02:50.926">我が</span><span begin="02:50.926" end="02:52.457">子等よ</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:46.869" end="02:52.465"><span begin="02:46.869" end="02:48.498">(走れどただ</span><span begin="02:48.498" end="02:50.030">走れども</span><span begin="02:50.030" end="02:52.465">辿り着けずに)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">奔跑、奔跑、却从未达到</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hasi re do tada hasi re domo tado ri tu ke zu ni</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">走在路上的芸芸众生啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mi chi wo a yu mu wa ga ko ra yo</span></p><p begin="02:53.035" end="02:59.030" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="02:53.035" end="02:55.015">其の物</span><span begin="02:55.015" end="02:56.607">語を</span><span begin="02:56.607" end="02:59.030">風に説き</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:53.472" end="02:59.051"><span begin="02:53.472" end="02:55.006">(登れども</span><span begin="02:55.006" end="02:56.620">登れども</span><span begin="02:56.620" end="02:59.051">墜ちて爪剥げ)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">攀登、攀登、手脚血肉模糊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">nobo re domo nobo re domo o ti te tume ha ge</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">请将那故事与风倾诉</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so no mo no ga ta ri wo ka ze ni to ki</span></p><p begin="02:59.817" end="03:05.416" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:59.817" end="03:01.410">いつか</span><span begin="03:01.410" end="03:03.057">天に</span><span begin="03:03.057" end="03:05.416">捧げよう</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:59.840" end="03:05.289"><span begin="02:59.840" end="03:01.496">(戦えども</span><span begin="03:01.496" end="03:03.033">戦えど</span><span begin="03:03.033" end="03:05.289">癒えぬ傷だけ)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">战斗、战斗、留不愈之伤</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">tataka e domo tataka e do i e nu kizu dake</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在未来的某一天把它献祭于天空吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">i tsu ka te n ni sa sa ge yo u</span></p><p begin="03:20.426" end="03:26.368" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="03:20.426" end="03:21.867">全ての</span><span begin="03:21.867" end="03:23.432">出会いは</span><span begin="03:23.432" end="03:24.127">離別</span><span begin="03:24.127" end="03:26.368">に向かい始まる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所有的相聚都向着离别而开始</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">su be te no de a i wa ri be tsu ni mu ka i ha ji ma ru</span></p><p begin="03:26.844" end="03:32.781" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="03:26.844" end="03:28.341">其れでも</span><span begin="03:28.421" end="03:29.917">人は</span><span begin="03:29.917" end="03:30.623">誰か</span><span begin="03:30.623" end="03:32.781">の傍で生きたい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使这样 人们也想依偎在他人的身旁</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so no re de mo hi to wa da re ka no bo u de i ki ta i</span></p><p begin="03:34.081" end="03:40.304" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="03:34.081" end="03:35.259">裏切られ</span><span begin="03:35.259" end="03:36.575">侮辱され</span><span begin="03:37.400" end="03:40.304">足蹴にされ心を壊されて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">被背叛 被侮辱 心灵被践踏得千疮百孔</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">u ra re bu jo ku sa re a shi ge ni sa re ko ko ro wo ko wa sa re te</span></p><p begin="03:40.538" end="03:46.331" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="03:40.538" end="03:43.142">裂けるくらい叫んでも</span><span begin="03:43.871" end="03:46.331">声は出なくて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">撕心裂肺地喊叫却发不出一丝声音</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sa ke ru ku ra i sa ke n de mo ko e wa de na ku te</span></p><p begin="03:47.069" end="03:53.459" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="03:47.069" end="03:49.682">生きる事を否定され</span><span begin="03:50.448" end="03:53.459">幾度死のうと決意していても</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">即使被否定了自身的存在价值 即使几度决意赴死</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">i ki ru ko to wo hi te i sa re i ku do shi no u to ke tsu i shi te i te mo</span></p><p begin="03:53.761" end="03:58.998" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="03:53.761" end="03:56.099">這い上がって繰り返し</span><span begin="03:56.670" end="03:58.998">願い叫ぶ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">也会一次次站起来 祈祷着 呐喊着</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ha i a ga tte ku ri ka e shi ne ga i sa ke bu</span></p><p begin="04:15.110" end="04:16.917" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L30">音も亡く灯火が消え<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">灯火静静地熄灭了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">o to mo na ku to mo shi bi ga ki e</span></p><p begin="04:18.309" end="04:19.999" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L31">深い闇に沈み込んだ果て<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">沉入了深深的黑暗之底</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">fu ka i ya mi ni shi zu mi ko n da ha te</span></p><p begin="04:22.141" end="04:26.182" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="04:22.141" end="04:22.766">其処に…</span><span begin="04:23.752" end="04:26.182">冥府に咲くひとつの桜が在る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在那...冥府里盛开着一株樱花</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so ko ni...me i fu ni sa ku hi to tsu no sa ku ra ga a ru</span></p><p begin="04:29.262" end="04:35.022" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="04:29.262" end="04:32.240">花弁は数多の死を映して仄かに染まり、</span><span begin="04:33.509" end="04:35.022">地に落ちては紅く染まる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">花瓣映照着无数的死 染上苍白的颜色 随即又落地染红</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ka be n wa a ma ta no shi wo u tsu shi te ho no ka ni so ma ri、chi ni o chi te wa a ka ku so ma ru</span></p><p begin="04:36.992" end="04:41.663" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="04:36.992" end="04:39.339">暖かい春風に舞う幾つもの死を、</span><span begin="04:40.281" end="04:41.663">あなたは奇麗だと云う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你说“在暖洋洋的春风中飘舞着的无数的‘死’十分美丽”</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a ta ta ka i ha ru ka ze ni ma u i ku tsu mo no shi wo、a na ta wa ki re i da to ku mo u</span></p><p begin="04:43.162" end="04:48.714" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="04:43.162" end="04:44.560">それがとても嬉しくて、</span><span begin="04:45.505" end="04:46.139">私は…</span><span begin="04:46.765" end="04:48.714">花弁の数だけ死を誘う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">好高兴 于是我...将引来与花瓣数量相当的“死”</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so re ga to te mo u re shi ku te、wa ta shi wa...ka be n no ka zu da ke shi wo sa so u</span></p><p begin="04:50.352" end="04:54.966" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="04:50.352" end="04:52.488">こんなにも美しく咲く最期なら、</span><span begin="04:53.233" end="04:54.966">彼等も報われたでしょう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在这般美丽盛开的最后 他们也会取得相应的报应吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ko n na ni mo u tsu ku shi ku sa ku sa i go na ra、ka re ra mo mu ku wa re ta de sho u</span></p><p begin="04:56.582" end="04:57.875" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L37">西行妖<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">西行妖啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ni shi gyo u yo u</span></p><p begin="05:00.384" end="05:03.509" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="05:00.384" end="05:01.323">今宵もまた、</span><span begin="05:01.756" end="05:03.509">紫月の下に咲き乱れる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">今宵 就在这紫月之下再度绽放吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ko yo i mo ma ta、mu ra sa ki ga tsu no shi ta ni sa ki mi da re ru</span></p><p begin="05:07.434" end="05:08.936" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L39">思い思いに抗えど<span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:06.385" end="05:11.920"><span begin="05:06.385" end="05:07.882">(願えども</span><span begin="05:07.882" end="05:09.494">願えども</span><span begin="05:09.494" end="05:11.920">願い叶わず)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">祈祷、祈祷、愿不能实现</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">nega e domo nega e domo nega i kana wa zu</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">思念 思念  无法抵抗</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">o mo i o mo i ni a ra ga e do</span></p><p begin="05:10.424" end="05:12.644" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L40">残酷なセカイは等しく降り掛かり<span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:06.434" end="05:11.838"><span begin="05:06.434" end="05:07.887">(願えども</span><span begin="05:07.887" end="05:09.534">願えども</span><span begin="05:09.534" end="05:11.838">願い叶わず)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">祈祷、祈祷、愿不能实现</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">nega e domo nega e domo nega i kana wa zu</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">残酷的世界也终会作为代价而降临的</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">za n ko ku na se ka i wa hi to shi ku o ri ka ka ri</span></p><p begin="05:14.591" end="05:19.157" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L41"><span begin="05:14.591" end="05:15.453">去れど人は、</span><span begin="05:16.608" end="05:19.157">今を生きるより他に道は無い</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:12.917" end="05:18.502"><span begin="05:12.917" end="05:14.511">(走れどただ</span><span begin="05:14.511" end="05:16.026">走れども</span><span begin="05:16.026" end="05:18.502">辿り着ずに)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">奔跑、奔跑、却从未到达</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hasi re do tada hasi re domo tado ri tu ke ni</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而逝去的人们啊 除了继续活于当下别无他法</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sa re do hi to wa、i ma wo i ki ru yo ri ho ka ni mi chi wa na i ni</span></p><p begin="05:20.725" end="05:24.178" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L42"><span begin="05:20.725" end="05:21.651">あなたも廻り</span><span begin="05:22.481" end="05:24.178">そして舞い散る</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:19.434" end="05:24.655"><span begin="05:19.434" end="05:20.920">(贖えど</span><span begin="05:20.920" end="05:22.562">贖えど</span><span begin="05:22.562" end="05:24.655">罪は消えずに)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">救赎、救赎、罪没有消除</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">agana e do agana e do tumi ha ki e zu ni</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“你也将轮回 并化作花瓣飘舞”</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a na ta mo ma wa ri、so shi te ma i chi ru</span></p><p begin="05:26.614" end="05:30.773" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L43"><span begin="05:26.614" end="05:26.866">——</span><span begin="05:26.580" end="05:27.315">死奏憐音、</span><span begin="05:29.420" end="05:30.773">玲瓏ノ終</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:25.794" end="05:31.150"><span begin="05:25.794" end="05:27.506">(廻れどただ</span><span begin="05:27.506" end="05:28.988">廻れども</span><span begin="05:28.988" end="05:31.150">終は視得亡い)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">徘徊、徘徊、看不到终点</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mawa re do tada mawa re domo tui ha si doku na i</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">——死奏怜音、玲珑之终</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">——shi so u re n o to、re i ro u no o wa ri</span></p><p begin="05:32.294" end="05:38.145" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L44"><span begin="05:32.294" end="05:33.872">咲かせ</span><span begin="05:33.872" end="05:35.415">咲かせ</span><span begin="05:35.415" end="05:38.145">報われぬ</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:32.225" end="05:37.979"><span begin="05:32.225" end="05:33.808">(歌えども</span><span begin="05:33.808" end="05:35.499">歌えども</span><span begin="05:35.499" end="05:37.979">歌は届かず)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">歌唱、歌唱、你却听不见</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">uta e domo uta e domo uta ha todo ka zu</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">盛开、盛开、却不得报应</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sa ka se sa ka se mu ku wa re nu</span></p><p begin="05:38.725" end="05:44.354" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L45"><span begin="05:38.725" end="05:40.320">道を</span><span begin="05:40.320" end="05:41.905">歩む</span><span begin="05:41.905" end="05:42.858">我が</span><span begin="05:42.858" end="05:44.354">子等よ</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:38.830" end="05:44.689"><span begin="05:38.830" end="05:40.421">(手にしても</span><span begin="05:40.421" end="05:42.039">手にしても</span><span begin="05:42.039" end="05:44.689">壊れてしまう)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">获得、获得、终将毁坏啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">te ni si te mo te ni si te mo kowa re te simau</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">走在路上的芸芸众生啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mi chi wo a yu mu wa ga ko ra yo</span></p><p begin="05:44.972" end="05:51.033" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L46"><span begin="05:44.972" end="05:46.879">其の物</span><span begin="05:46.879" end="05:48.426">語を</span><span begin="05:48.426" end="05:51.033">抱きしめて</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:45.363" end="05:50.931"><span begin="05:45.363" end="05:46.803">(贖えど</span><span begin="05:46.803" end="05:48.417">贖えど</span><span begin="05:48.417" end="05:50.931">罪は消えずに)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">救赎、救赎、罪没有消除</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">agana e do agana e do tumi ha ki e zu ni</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">请将这故事紧拥着</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so no mo no ga ta ri wo da ki shi me te</span></p><p begin="05:51.683" end="05:57.834" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L47"><span begin="05:51.683" end="05:53.363">いつか</span><span begin="05:53.363" end="05:54.994">天に</span><span begin="05:54.994" end="05:57.834">届けよう</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="05:51.716" end="05:57.148"><span begin="05:51.716" end="05:53.444">(廻れどただ</span><span begin="05:53.444" end="05:54.994">廻れども</span><span begin="05:54.994" end="05:57.148">終は視得亡い)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">徘徊、徘徊、看不到终点</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">mawa re do tada mawa re domo tui ha si doku na i</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在未来的某一天把它传达到天空吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">i tsu ka te n ni to do ke yo u</span></p><p begin="06:02.177" end="06:05.586" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L48"><span begin="06:02.177" end="06:03.039">それでも人は</span><span begin="06:03.798" end="06:05.586">醜くも生きようとする</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就算如此 人们也想丑陋地生存着</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so re de mo hi to wa、mi ni ku mo i ki yo u to su ru</span></p><p begin="06:08.470" end="06:12.930" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L49"><span begin="06:08.470" end="06:09.396">それを私は</span><span begin="06:11.244" end="06:12.930">とても美しいと思う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对此 我——觉得那是如此的美丽......</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so re wo wa ta shi wa、to te mo u tsu ku shi i to o mo u</span></p><p begin="00:00.000" end="00:00.000" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L50">来自网易云源<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">原翻译：网易云@hourainingyou</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">TTML歌词作者（音译补全、打轴、背景人声、对唱人声）：Telegram@Azusa_mikan</span></p></div></body></tt>